        VT["verify_templates.py (make verify-templates; pins chezmoi --source to current repo)<br/>verify_mermaids.py (make verify-mermaids; .mermaids census + overview anchors)<br/>verify_bin_surface.py (make verify-bin-surface; ~/bin completions/docs/catalog + exact token matching + home/exact_lib orphans)<br/>verify_docs_navigation.py (make verify-docs-navigation; docs/reference links + catalog rows)<br/>verify_agent_file_sizes.py (make verify-agent-file-sizes; exact_dot_agents reference .md under 20480B view limit, SKILL.md exempt)"]:::misc
